&lt;p&gt;This ties into my previous post, where I spoke about &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://davevoyles.azurewebsites.net/get-game-app-xbox-one/&#34;&gt;how to get your game or app on Xbox One.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Microsoft unveiled quiet a bit of information regarding SmartGlass during BUILD 2012, and much of it is available **&lt;a href=&#34;http://video.ch9.ms/sessions/build/2012/2-028.pptx&#34;&gt;via this Power Point presentation.&lt;/a&gt;**Ignore most of the C++ in there; I never had to touch any of that. All of my work was done via JavaScript and it worked fine.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
